      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p></p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.R8WbK8lNtte4pQtL]{Dither}</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">20</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Scene</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>When you cast this spell, you must declare an Action type (besides Attack). For the spell’s duration, whenever the Target takes the declared Action, they lose hit points equal to their level.</p><p>Once this has occurred 3 times, this spells effects end.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.frwB8cqmoLZVu6UE]{Discompose}</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">20</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Scene</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Target suffers a <strong>-1</strong> penalty to their Accuracy or Magic Checks. This penalty increases to <strong>-2</strong> at if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, and to <strong>-3</strong> if you are <strong>level 40 or higher</strong>.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.KzqKXsyjxACBAQmQ]{Halt} @ICON[offensive]</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">5 × T</span></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\">Up to five creatures</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Each Target hit by this spell suffers <strong>slow</strong>.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.cdtvadDdUwGhO7qa]{Inversion} @ICON[offensive]</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">20</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Scene</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Targets current <strong>Dexterity</strong> and <strong>Might</strong> die sizes are switched, as are their <strong>Insight</strong> and <strong>Willpower</strong>.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.2gy7ociDp2eHQ742]{Malady}</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Up to 20</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Roll 1d6 once for every 10 Mind Points spent when casting this spell. Resolve each effect.</p><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>1</strong></p></td><td><p>Nothing happens.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>2</strong></p></td><td><p>Target suffers <strong>slow</strong>.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>3</strong></p></td><td><p>Target suffers <strong>dazed</strong>.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>4</strong></p></td><td><p>Target suffers <strong>weak</strong>.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>5</strong></p></td><td><p>Target suffers <strong>shaken</strong>.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>6</strong></p></td><td><p>Target suffers your choice of either <strong>dazed</strong>, <strong>shaken</strong>, <strong>slow</strong>, or <strong>weak</strong>.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.7ojEPaQ2cEgNweUG]{Regression}</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">20</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Any spells or effects on the Target that were acquired since the end of your last turn are lost. If an effect was acquired as a consequence of a change of state, such as being in Crisis or holding a specific item, it cannot be lost as a result of this spell.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.zdFoIGrhUXJ1WbrE]{Soften}</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">20</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Target becomes Vulnerable to the next source of damage they suffer.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.1Ar3BTf5nve7ptxV]{Shuffle} @ICON[offensive]</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">15</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Two creatures</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Targets swap their current Status Effects with one another. Willing Targets can choose to be hit by this spell regardless of the Magic Checks result.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.RuX8NHE2mtMJVB3D]{Stagger}</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">5 × T</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Up to five creatures</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Each Target hit by this spell suffers <strong>dazed</strong>.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.2FOoZ0zpwiRMzo9K]{Sunder} @ICON[offensive]</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">20</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Scene</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Targets Defense and Magic Defense are reduced by <strong>2</strong>.</p><p>Once the Target has been hit by <strong>3</strong> Attacks or Offensive Spells, this spells effect ends.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.oHFC8s1P56egdxpa]{Terrify} @ICON[offensive]</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">5 × T</span></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\">Up to five creatures</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Each Target hit by this spell suffers <strong>shaken</strong>.</p><p>.</p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:80px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:9px\"><td style=\"height:17px\" data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>Malefaction</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><strong> Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td data-colwidth=\"160\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-homebrew.homebrew-skills.Item.F6TDpuqvXRpqDGiQ]{Wither} @ICON[offensive]</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">5 × T</span></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Up to five creatures</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><p>Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Each Target hit by this spell suffers <strong>weak</strong>.</p><p>.</p>"
